<http://www.example.org/meddevice#Manufacturer> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Manufacturer"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/meddevice#MedicalDevice
<http://www.example.org/meddevice#MedicalDevice> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
