<http://www.example.org/meddevice#Recall> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Corrective action that removes or replaces affected devices."@en .
<http://www.example.org/meddevice#Recall> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Recall"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/meddevice#RegulatoryFramework
