<http://www.example.org/meddevice#RegulatoryFramework> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Regulatory Framework"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/meddevice#Risk
<http://www.example.org/meddevice#Risk> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.example.org/meddevice#Risk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.example.org/meddevice#Entity> .
<http://www.example.org/meddevice#Risk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Potential harm associated with a device."@en .
<http://www.example.org/meddevice#Risk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Risk"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/meddevice#RiskClass
<http://www.example.org/meddevice#RiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.example.org/meddevice#RiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.example.org/meddevice#Entity> .
