<http://www.example.org/meddevice#SafetyAlert> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Formal safety communication issued by the manufacturer."@en .
<http://www.example.org/meddevice#SafetyAlert> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Safety Alert"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/meddevice#SeriousIncident
<http://www.example.org/meddevice#SeriousIncident> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
