<http://www.example.org/meddevice#SeriousIncident> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Incident that led or might have led to serious harm or death."@en .
<http://www.example.org/meddevice#SeriousIncident> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Serious Incident"@en .
